1:03:22.615 --> 1:03:27.153
We’re also pleased to announce 
the release of a new brochure 


1:03:27.153 --> 1:03:31.890
entitled 
Answers to 10 Questions Young People Ask.


1:03:31.890 --> 1:03:36.528
The content of this 32-page, 
full-color brochure 


1:03:36.528 --> 1:03:40.533
is based on articles 
in Awake! and the two volumes 


1:03:40.533 --> 1:03:45.003
of Questions Young People Ask
—Answers That Work, as well as 


1:03:45.003 --> 1:03:49.741
the “Young People Ask” articles 
on the jw.org website. 


1:03:49.742 --> 1:03:53.412
This new brochure 
will be particularly helpful 


1:03:53.412 --> 1:03:58.017
to those who speak a language 
in which that material is not available. 


1:03:58.017 --> 1:04:02.622
However, all young people 
can benefit from this new brochure 


1:04:02.622 --> 1:04:07.627
because the original articles 
have been updated and rewritten.


1:04:07.627 --> 1:04:12.097
Each section of the brochure 
addresses one question. 


1:04:12.097 --> 1:04:16.969
After stating the question, 
the section begins with a pointed statement 


1:04:16.968 --> 1:04:19.838
under the feature 
“Why It Matters,” 


1:04:19.838 --> 1:04:23.708
letting the reader know 
why that question is relevant. 


1:04:23.708 --> 1:04:28.246
Then, a “What Would You Do?” 
scenario is presented, 


1:04:28.247 --> 1:04:31.450
putting the reader 
in a hypothetical situation 


1:04:31.450 --> 1:04:33.585
related to the topic. 


1:04:33.585 --> 1:04:36.522
After discussing various principles, 


1:04:36.522 --> 1:04:40.325
Scriptural advice 
directs the reader to the best answers 


1:04:40.325 --> 1:04:42.862
for that particular question.


1:04:42.862 --> 1:04:45.965
The 10 Questions brochure 
is interactive, 


1:04:45.965 --> 1:04:48.467
allowing the reader 
to write responses 


1:04:48.467 --> 1:04:50.870
to the various questions presented. 


1:04:50.870 --> 1:04:55.207
The final topic, 
“How Can the Bible Help Me?,” 


1:04:55.207 --> 1:04:59.345
is designed to invite readers 
who are not Jehovah’s Witnesses 


1:04:59.345 --> 1:05:01.480
to accept a Bible study. 


1:05:01.480 --> 1:05:04.483
The brochure 
makes numerous references 


1:05:04.483 --> 1:05:06.818
to the jw.org website 


1:05:06.818 --> 1:05:11.090
and directs readers to more information 
that can be found there. 


1:05:11.090 --> 1:05:14.893
Also, the brochure 
is designed in such a way 


1:05:14.893 --> 1:05:19.031
that young people can be comfortable 
sharing it with their peers 


1:05:19.032 --> 1:05:21.567
and with others in the ministry.


1:05:21.567 --> 1:05:26.505
This brochure 
is already approved for translation 


1:05:26.505 --> 1:05:30.075
into 324 languages. 


1:05:30.075 --> 1:05:35.080
Of these languages, 
223 do not produce Awake! 


1:05:35.080 --> 1:05:38.750
and 262 have not produced 


1:05:38.750 --> 1:05:40.753
the Young People Ask books. 


1:05:40.753 --> 1:05:44.890
So we expect that Answers 
to 10 Questions Young People Ask 


1:05:44.890 --> 1:05:47.627
will help 
many more youths benefit 


1:05:47.627 --> 1:05:50.697
from the Bible’s practical wisdom.


1:05:50.697 --> 1:05:54.500
