at the conclusion of this program.


1:06:14.720 --> 1:06:17.723
Before we finish, 
we’d like to share 


1:06:17.723 --> 1:06:22.126
this postcard from the city 
of L’viv, in Ukraine. 


1:06:22.127 --> 1:06:27.065
The city has approximately 
800,000 inhabitants and is surrounded 


1:06:27.065 --> 1:06:29.068
by beautiful forests. 


1:06:29.068 --> 1:06:34.073
But L’viv is also the home of 5,000 
of our dear brothers and sisters. 


1:06:34.073 --> 1:06:36.441
One of the 49 congregations 


1:06:36.442 --> 1:06:40.645
in L’viv 
is the Topolna Tsentralnyi Congregation. 


1:06:40.645 --> 1:06:44.017
This congregation 
has 107 publishers, 


1:06:44.017 --> 1:06:47.019
including 42 regular pioneers. 


1:06:47.018 --> 1:06:52.156
Last year, during the month of August, 
70 percent of them took part 


1:06:52.157 --> 1:06:55.995
in some form of pioneer service, 
despite the fact that this congregation 


1:06:55.995 --> 1:07:00.365
has [one of] the smallest 
territories in the city. 


1:07:00.365 --> 1:07:03.368
Public witnessing using carts 
has proven very effective, 


1:07:03.368 --> 1:07:05.705
and the publishers also cover 


1:07:05.705 --> 1:07:10.375
remote territories 
in small villages outside the city. 


1:07:10.375 --> 1:07:14.113
The publishers 
of the Topolna Tsentralnyi Congregation 


1:07:14.113 --> 1:07:16.648
send their warm Christian love 


1:07:16.648 --> 1:07:20.351
to all of us worldwide. 


